data.description: Gorgeous pre-owned home that shows like a model home! Barely lived in but dressed to the 9's! All the upgrades & final details have been handled. Move in & start living your best life! Granite countertops, built-in kitchen with extended breakfast bar, wood plank & tile flooring, recessed lighting, crown molding, art niche, 3 bedrooms plus office with French doors & closet which could double as a FOURTH bedroom, Wood-burning fireplace with raised rock hearth & wood mantel, double sinks in primary bathroom with separate garden tub & walk-in shower, walk-in closet, raised ceilings, covered porch & patio, landscaping, wood fence, sprinkler system, additional decking in attic for storage, 2 car garage. ALSO INCLUDES window coverings - blinds AND stainless steel refrigerator. Welcome home!
